        {
            "id": 6010161,
            "title": "〈熱門股〉華碩AI伺服器、PC升級引擎發動 法人聯手連4買",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>PC 品牌華碩 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2357:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2357\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2357-TW</a>) 近期獲小摩點讚，認為在 PC 部分，將會受惠於升級以及電競刺激、AI 伺服器則有利潤可期，而華碩也在近期推出 RTX 筆電全線新品，並獲得法人青睞，華碩 6 日股價收 645 元，周漲幅約 3%、周成交量 18393 張，三大法人呈連四買，買超 1168 張。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010161%2Fl%2Fcea3330aa7a42d36521f1c7206f8f387.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010161%2Fl%2Fcea3330aa7a42d36521f1c7206f8f387.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010161%2Fl%2Fcea3330aa7a42d36521f1c7206f8f387.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010161%2Fl%2Fcea3330aa7a42d36521f1c7206f8f387.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010161%2Fl%2Fcea3330aa7a42d36521f1c7206f8f387.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010161%2Fl%2Fcea3330aa7a42d36521f1c7206f8f387.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010161%2Fl%2Fcea3330aa7a42d36521f1c7206f8f387.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010161%2Fl%2Fcea3330aa7a42d36521f1c7206f8f387.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010161%2Fl%2Fcea3330aa7a42d36521f1c7206f8f387.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010161%2Fl%2Fcea3330aa7a42d36521f1c7206f8f387.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010161%2Fl%2Fcea3330aa7a42d36521f1c7206f8f387.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010161%2Fl%2Fcea3330aa7a42d36521f1c7206f8f387.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010161%2Fl%2Fcea3330aa7a42d36521f1c7206f8f387.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010161%2Fl%2Fcea3330aa7a42d36521f1c7206f8f387.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010161%2Fl%2Fcea3330aa7a42d36521f1c7206f8f387.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010161%2Fl%2Fcea3330aa7a42d36521f1c7206f8f387.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010161%2Fl%2Fcea3330aa7a42d36521f1c7206f8f387.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">〈熱門股〉華碩AI伺服器、PC升級引擎發動 法人聯手連4買。(圖：shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>小摩近期出具「個人電腦（PC）與伺服器產業」報告指出，根據戴爾及惠普，商用電腦將受惠 Windows11 升級、AI PC 上市潮，動能成長強勁，而在 PC 部分看好華碩，認為華碩將受惠於電競遊戲動能，在 PC 和 AI 伺服器都有所成長。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>另外，華碩近期積極推出 RTX 系列產品，包括 RTX 5050、5060、5070 等電競、創作者筆電，儘管面對美國關稅波動，但在 GPU 以及筆電升級需求下，仍對第二季展望樂觀，在 PC 及板卡、顯示卡等零組件業務，皆看好雙位數季成長。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>伺服器業務部份，華碩以亞太市場為大宗，但近期積極切入北美市場，在接下來的新品 GB200、GB300 伺服器皆為北美客戶，並力拚伺服器營收占比從近雙位數達到 15% 的目標。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>觀察華碩近期籌碼動向，三大法人呈連 4 買，買超 1168 張；外資連 3 買，買超 1201 張；投信連 2 賣轉買，買超 16 張；自營商連 3 買，買超 92 張。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img data-cnyeschart=\"cnyeschart\" src=\"https://so.cnyes.com/mobilechart/MobileChart.aspx?markettype=twstock&amp;charttype1=kchart&amp;stockcode=2357&amp;imgwidth=580&amp;imgheight=500&amp;bgcolor=2\"/>\n<figcaption>華碩日 K 線圖</figcaption>\n</figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p> </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
